nake_case conventions and semantic clarity principles. Data classifications are appropriate with confidential tags applied to sensitive business information (penalties, audit results, costs, corrective actions). I did not include any technical ETL attributes, calculated metrics, or speculative fields. The schema is production-ready and comprehensive for a compliance_requirement data product in the contract domain. Minor deduction for potential edge cases in highly specialized compliance scenarios that may exist in niche regulatory contexts, but all mainstream compliance requirement attributes are covered."
